de.uni.bamberg.wiai.minf.forflow.datagenerator.model.datastructure
Class FacetSimplified

java.lang.Object
  de.uni.bamberg.wiai.minf.forflow.datagenerator.model.datastructure.FacetSimplified

public class FacetSimplified
extends java.lang.Object

This class represents a simplified version of MetaAttribute. It has only attributes important for doing a special kind of job. The class is used only for specifying null values and therefore we do not make much use of the full attribute list.

It holds the attribute name of the original meta attribute class, it's class name where it belongs and a flag indicating the null value status.
